{"title":"笑脸难装","authors":["池北偶"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":3,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑脸难装"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池北偶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你去讲“亲善”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群众把你赶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你去表“友好”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学生喊滚蛋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军警保护你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥刀又开枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群众驱不散，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只好放泪弹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未料波及你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑脸无法装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抿住大鼻子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼泪落两行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"确实煞风景，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"体面受影响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以后再出使，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"防毒面具千万带身旁。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}